<body>

  {{#if signed_in}}
    {{> menu id="about" name=name surname=surname}}
  {{else}}
    {{> welcomemenu id="about"}}
  {{/if}}

  <main>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="card mt-3">
        <div class="card-header"> <h3>Critical Restaurant</h3></div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p>
            {{#if name}}{{name}} {{surname}}{{else}}Hey{{/if}}, have you ever been disappointed after trying a new restaurant? Have you ever thought to yourself "Wow, this place was really amazing, I wish I could tell the whole world!"?
          </p>
          <p>
            If you said yes to one of these questions, then look no further! This small web app can satisfy all your rating and ranking needs concerning food establishments in your area!
          </p>

          <p>
            Features include:
            <ul>
              <li>The ability to review all past experiences in restaurants (after you have logged in or created an account of course :))</li>
              <li>A list of all restaurants in your area, ordered by ratings of other people</li>
              <li>An interactive map containing all restaurants</li>
              <li>A search Function where you can search for restaurants, dishes (or both) and filter concerning stars</li>
              <li>The ability the add restaurants and dishes for each restaurant</li>
            </ul>
            ...and many more!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>  
  </main>
  
  {{>footer}}

</body>